      "text": "Enable Cross-region replication of Azure NetApp Files volumes",
      "description": "Azure NetApp Files replication offers data protection by allowing asynchronous cross-region volume replication for application failover in case of regional outages. Volumes can be replicated across regions, not concurrently with cross-zone replication. Note that failover is a manual process.",
